How to get first freelancing client?
1. Proposal must be concise to convince buyer 
(use AI Tool)
2. If you create gigs on fiverr make sure that SEO is done correct
3. choose the highly ranked gigs, you can check out their description, check out their title and also create similar kind of gigs
   you can copy paste if you want to
4. It is highly recommended to ceate a strong freelancing portfolio where you mention all your projects
that you can share with your proposals or you can add to your gigs, this will increase chances of getting your first freelancing client
5. After working, get good review

